This is myb first effort to build a social room for conncting people.

This room has login capabilities and register capabilities for new users!
This room also provides the ability to lock (session login) certain pages

The user can have:
Upload photos in a gallery
Add friends in a list
Add comments (public or private)

There is an administrator with 
name:admin
passwd:admin

Administrator can change user privilleges,adds comments and creates galleries

Simple user can only upload images and add friends!

There are some ajax capabilities in the new login form!

Future Work:
More secure links in sessions
Better user interfaces
More capabilities in users
Better administration menu
Localization in diffrent languages

Some data are in Greek!!!!